# GRAPHICS::SET_PARTICLE_FX_NON_LOOPED_EMITTER_SIZE

## Summary
Sets the size of the emitter domain of the next non looped particle effect

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** overrideSizeX
* **FLOAT** overrideSizeY
* **FLOAT** overrideSizeZ
